Machine learning 
>Ability of the computer to learn themselves wihtout being explicitly programmed .
Machines learn themselves in machine learning .
****
deep learning is a sub branch of machine learning and machine learning is a sub unit of artifiicial intelligence .
****

Learning is done on the basis of the previous input of data .

In ML:
data(input) -> machine -> program on its own 
data needs to be high precesion and accruate .

Error margin  : Difference between the machine generated output and the actual data . 
Error margin has to be reduced to get the ideal output .
